918
00:44:46,059 --> 00:44:47,800
[SPEAKER_00] ni zašto, jer mi je ovo jako drago.

919
00:44:47,800 --> 00:44:49,480
[SPEAKER_00] Opoziv Nine obuljen.

920
00:44:49,480 --> 00:44:53,360
[SPEAKER_00] Gdje su ovi ostali?

921
00:44:53,360 --> 00:44:55,760
[SPEAKER_00] Evo, SDP ne da na Ninu obuljen.

922
00:44:55,760 --> 00:44:57,679
[SPEAKER_00] Pogledajte još jednom, hajde, žadonče.

923
00:44:57,679 --> 00:44:59,960
[SPEAKER_00] Evo, dajte mi to komentirajte.

924
00:44:59,960 --> 00:45:02,599
[SPEAKER_00] Šarli Krk, Nina obuljen,

925
00:45:02,599 --> 00:45:04,579
