930
00:45:14,840 --> 00:45:16,079
[SPEAKER_03] to je moje suho zlato.

931
00:45:16,079 --> 00:45:19,019
[SPEAKER_03] Tako je premijer, predsjednik vlade,

932
00:45:19,019 --> 00:45:20,800
[SPEAKER_03] rekao da je Nina obuljen,

933
00:45:20,800 --> 00:45:22,039
[SPEAKER_03] njegovo suho zlato.

934
00:45:22,039 --> 00:45:24,340
[SPEAKER_03] Ta Nina obuljen,

935
00:45:24,340 --> 00:45:26,440
[SPEAKER_03] 400 tisuća eura,

936
00:45:26,440 --> 00:45:28,500
[SPEAKER_03] 400 tisuća eura,

937
00:45:28,500 --> 00:45:31,380
[SPEAKER_03] tijekom njezina mandata,

938
00:45:31,380 --> 00:45:34,019
[SPEAKER_03] šefovanja Ministarstva kulture,

939
00:45:34,019 --> 00:45:36,099
[SPEAKER_03] je dala ljudima

940
00:45:36,099 --> 00:45:39,840
[SPEAKER_03] koji su projugoslavenski nastrojeni

941
00:45:39,840 --> 00:45:40,760
[SPEAKER_03] u svakom pogledu.

942
00:45:40,760 --> 00:45:42,039
[SPEAKER_03] Ja ću ovo argumentirat.

943
00:45:42,039 --> 00:45:42,920
[SPEAKER_03] Dakle,

944
00:45:42,920 --> 00:45:46,380
[SPEAKER_03] gospodin Jergović je dobio nešto više od 100 tisuća eura,

945
00:45:46,380 --> 00:45:47,039
[SPEAKER_03] ako se ne veram,

946
00:45:47,039 --> 00:45:48,320
[SPEAKER_03] 106 tisuća eura.

947
00:45:48,320 --> 00:45:49,639
[SPEAKER_03] 106 tisuća eura.

948
00:45:49,639 --> 00:45:51,179
[SPEAKER_03] Ante Tomić,

949
00:45:51,179 --> 00:45:52,280
[SPEAKER_03] slušajte ta imena.

950
00:45:52,280 --> 00:45:52,619
[SPEAKER_03] Dakle,

951
00:45:52,619 --> 00:45:53,679
[SPEAKER_03] znamo kako oni pišu,

952
00:45:53,679 --> 00:45:54,579
[SPEAKER_03] o čemu oni pišu.

953
00:45:55,320 --> 00:45:57,139
[SPEAKER_03] nekoliko desetaka tisuća eura,

954
00:45:57,139 --> 00:45:58,159
[SPEAKER_03] Slavenka,

955
00:45:58,159 --> 00:45:58,800
[SPEAKER_03] Drakulić,

956
00:45:58,800 --> 00:46:00,579
[SPEAKER_03] nekoliko desetaka tisuća eura.

957
00:46:00,579 --> 00:46:01,360
[SPEAKER_03] Dakle,

958
00:46:01,360 --> 00:46:02,480
[SPEAKER_03] cijela ta ekipa,

959
00:46:02,480 --> 00:46:03,840
[SPEAKER_03] 400 tisuća eura,

960
00:46:03,840 --> 00:46:05,420
[SPEAKER_03] a sad slušite nešto jako zanimljivo.

961
00:46:05,420 --> 00:46:07,559
[SPEAKER_03] Stranka možemo.

962
00:46:07,559 --> 00:46:10,139
[SPEAKER_03] Sandra Benčić je potpisnica

963
00:46:10,139 --> 00:46:13,199
[SPEAKER_03] Jugoslavenske zajedničke deklaracije

964
