965
00:46:16,860 --> 00:46:18,079
[SPEAKER_03] U Hrvatskom saboru,

966
00:46:18,079 --> 00:46:19,079
[SPEAKER_03] ja sam sjedio tada,

967
00:46:19,079 --> 00:46:20,280
[SPEAKER_03] to sam rekao ovdje kod vas,

968
