[SPEAKER_03] kaj ćemo mi raspravljati

971
00:46:25,539 --> 00:46:26,519
[SPEAKER_03] o ovim glupostima.

972
00:46:26,519 --> 00:46:28,219
[SPEAKER_03] Za njih su gluposti

973
00:46:28,219 --> 00:46:29,539
[SPEAKER_03] hrvatski jezik.

974
00:46:29,539 --> 00:46:31,059
[SPEAKER_03] Jezik moje matere,

975
