995
00:47:04,739 --> 00:47:06,360
[SPEAKER_03] Mišlim da ih je osam ili devet,

996
00:47:06,360 --> 00:47:07,900
[SPEAKER_03] ali više od osamdeset posto.

997
00:47:07,900 --> 00:47:10,239
[SPEAKER_00] Sad ću ja na njihovom jeziku citirat Boru Čorbu.

998
00:47:10,239 --> 00:47:12,019
[SPEAKER_00] Znate koja je Sandra Benčić?

999
00:47:13,840 --> 00:47:15,619
[SPEAKER_00] Uša, vrinu bez filtera.

1000
00:47:15,619 --> 00:47:16,900
[SPEAKER_00] Loše mi ide srpski.

1001
00:47:16,900 --> 00:47:17,820
[SPEAKER_03] Da.

1002
00:47:17,820 --> 00:47:18,320
[SPEAKER_03] Ne veruša.

1003
00:47:18,320 --> 00:47:20,239
[SPEAKER_03] Dakle, stvarno je to velik problem.

1004
00:47:20,239 --> 00:47:21,320
[SPEAKER_03] Jer šta je priča?

1005
00:47:21,320 --> 00:47:22,539
[SPEAKER_03] Dakle, mi nemamo problem.

1006
00:47:22,539 --> 00:47:23,940
[SPEAKER_03] Oni cijelo vrijeme spiniraju.

1007
00:47:23,940 --> 00:47:26,460
[SPEAKER_03] Plenković i njegovo suho zlato.

1008
00:47:26,460 --> 00:47:27,400
[SPEAKER_03] Ministrica Obiljenja,

1009
00:47:27,400 --> 00:47:28,000
[SPEAKER_03] dajte molim vas,

1010
00:47:28,000 --> 00:47:29,159
[SPEAKER_03] svojako je važno radi istine,

1011
00:47:29,159 --> 00:47:29,820
[SPEAKER_03] ovo da ne zaboravim.

1012
00:47:29,820 --> 00:47:31,179
[SPEAKER_03] Moj kolega je Ivica Ledenko.

1013
00:47:31,179 --> 00:47:33,840
[SPEAKER_03] Dakle, ja sam govorio o Obiljenki

1014
00:47:33,840 --> 00:47:34,800
