1015
00:47:34,800 --> 00:47:36,679
[SPEAKER_03] Ja ne znam koliko puta je u Hrvatskom saboru

1016
00:47:36,679 --> 00:47:37,719
[SPEAKER_03] i na svojim društvenim mrežama.

1017
00:47:38,059 --> 00:47:39,380
[SPEAKER_03] I sad sam jako kritizirao.

1018
00:47:39,380 --> 00:47:40,760
[SPEAKER_03] Ali kolega Ledenko,

1019
00:47:40,760 --> 00:47:41,920
[SPEAKER_03] naš saborski zastupnik,

1020
00:47:41,920 --> 00:47:43,139
[SPEAKER_03] on je iz Šibenika,

1021
00:47:43,139 --> 00:47:45,780
