1022
00:47:45,780 --> 00:47:46,480
[SPEAKER_03] protiv nje.

1023
00:47:46,480 --> 00:47:47,579
[SPEAKER_03] Naravno ime kluba Mosta

1024
00:47:47,579 --> 00:47:48,699
[SPEAKER_03] i svi smo tu stali iza,

1025
00:47:48,699 --> 00:47:50,699
[SPEAKER_03] ali ovažno im je to bilo da kažem.

1026
00:47:50,699 --> 00:47:52,780
[SPEAKER_00] Pozdrav Ledenko i Škugoru

1027
00:47:52,780 --> 00:47:55,679
[SPEAKER_00] i imali smo izjavu ide u petak

1028
00:47:55,679 --> 00:47:56,420
[SPEAKER_00] cijela emisija.

1029
00:47:56,800 --> 00:47:58,840
[SPEAKER_03] Molim vas, samo što ovo jako mi je važno.

1030
00:47:58,840 --> 00:48:01,219
[SPEAKER_03] Dakle, priča Obiljenke,

1031
00:48:01,219 --> 00:48:02,039
[SPEAKER_03] jako je bitno ovo.

1032
00:48:02,039 --> 00:48:03,940
[SPEAKER_03] Dakle, onda oni spiniraju,

1033
00:48:03,940 --> 00:48:05,340
[SPEAKER_03] vi ste protiv kulture ovo.

1034
00:48:05,340 --> 00:48:06,599
[SPEAKER_03] Ne, apsolutno ne.

1035
00:48:06,599 --> 00:48:08,119
[SPEAKER_03] Ali ne s našim parama.

1036
00:48:08,119 --> 00:48:10,820
[SPEAKER_03] Ne s novcem hrvatskih obveznika,

1037
00:48:10,820 --> 00:48:11,400
[SPEAKER_03] poreznih.

1038
00:48:11,400 --> 00:48:14,500
[SPEAKER_03] I država ne smije sfinansirati program

1039
00:48:14,500 --> 00:48:16,159
[SPEAKER_03] koji napada hrvatske branitelje,

1040
00:48:16,159 --> 00:48:17,400
