1043
00:48:19,260 --> 00:48:21,519
[SPEAKER_03] A oni bez zažavnog novca ne bi postali.

1044
00:48:21,519 --> 00:48:22,139
[SPEAKER_03] Njih nema.

1045
00:48:22,139 --> 00:48:24,360
[SPEAKER_00] Pa naravno, kad niko pada ništa,

1046
00:48:24,360 --> 00:48:26,059
[SPEAKER_00] Thompson da kupe ljudi 500.000 kakar.

1047
00:48:26,059 --> 00:48:27,480
[SPEAKER_00] Pa ko će dati njima jedne lipe,

1048
00:48:27,480 --> 00:48:28,059
[SPEAKER_00] razumijete?

1049
00:48:28,059 --> 00:48:29,039
[SPEAKER_00] Dakle, oni bi propali.

1050
00:48:29,039 --> 00:48:30,619
[SPEAKER_00] Ali nije problem u njima.

1051
00:48:30,619 --> 00:48:33,559
[SPEAKER_00] Oni imaju pravo nas pljačkati

1052
00:48:33,559 --> 00:48:35,179
[SPEAKER_00] ako im to mi dopušta.

1053
00:48:35,179 --> 00:48:35,820
[SPEAKER_00] Slažem se.

1054
00:48:35,820 --> 00:48:38,940
[SPEAKER_00] Ali kako ljudi iz HDZ-a

1055
00:48:38,940 --> 00:48:40,880
[SPEAKER_00] istovremeno mogu biti

1056
00:48:40,880 --> 00:48:43,599
[SPEAKER_00] za Thomsona i za Frljića?

1057
00:48:43,599 --> 00:48:46,760
