1058
00:48:46,760 --> 00:48:49,719
[SPEAKER_00] Kako možeš isto dobno biti

1059
00:48:49,719 --> 00:48:52,980
[SPEAKER_00] za Thomsona i za Frljića?

1060
00:48:52,980 --> 00:48:55,340
