1063
00:49:00,940 --> 00:49:02,139
[SPEAKER_00] plaćaju.

1064
00:49:02,139 --> 00:49:05,179
[SPEAKER_03] Frljić je jako skandalozan

1065
00:49:05,179 --> 00:49:06,340
[SPEAKER_03] da budem umjeren.

1066
00:49:06,340 --> 00:49:08,960
[SPEAKER_03] Jedan ostrašćeni komunist

1067
00:49:08,960 --> 00:49:10,760
[SPEAKER_03] kojeg su potirali iz Poljske.

1068
00:49:10,760 --> 00:49:13,860
[SPEAKER_03] Dakle, on radi svoju umjetnost,

1069
00:49:13,860 --> 00:49:16,679
