1070
00:49:16,679 --> 00:49:18,239
[SPEAKER_03] nego da duboko vrijeđa

1071
00:49:18,239 --> 00:49:20,039
[SPEAKER_03] napose, naravno, kršćane.

1072
00:49:20,039 --> 00:49:21,559
[SPEAKER_03] Dakle, kada Isus,

1073
00:49:21,559 --> 00:49:23,519
[SPEAKER_03] Bože mi oprosti,

1074
00:49:23,519 --> 00:49:25,440
[SPEAKER_03] silazi iz križa i siluje časnu,

1075
00:49:25,440 --> 00:49:27,719
[SPEAKER_03] kada časna izvlači iz vagine

1076
00:49:27,719 --> 00:49:28,659
[SPEAKER_03] Hrvatsku zastavu,

1077
00:49:28,659 --> 00:49:29,900
[SPEAKER_03] to su Frljiće predstave.

1078
00:49:29,900 --> 00:49:31,280
[SPEAKER_03] Dakle, to je dno...

1079
00:49:31,280 --> 00:49:33,739
[SPEAKER_03] I to financira i dina obuljani gradovi,

1080
00:49:33,739 --> 00:49:34,900
[SPEAKER_03] povlaze, Šibenik.

1081
00:49:34,900 --> 00:49:35,679
[SPEAKER_03] Sigurno, vjerojatno.

1082
00:49:35,679 --> 00:49:36,460
[SPEAKER_03] Znači, sigurno.

1083
00:49:36,460 --> 00:49:37,639
[SPEAKER_03] Dakle, ne, sigurno.

1084
00:49:37,639 --> 00:49:39,179
[SPEAKER_03] Sad ne znam s kojom je točno

1085
00:49:39,179 --> 00:49:40,179
[SPEAKER_03] predstavom dolje bio.

1086
00:49:40,179 --> 00:49:42,039
[SPEAKER_03] Iako ova predstava o obitelji

1087
00:49:42,039 --> 00:49:42,860
[SPEAKER_03] koji je imao dolje,

1088
00:49:42,860 --> 00:49:44,099
[SPEAKER_03] onda je on rekao

1089
00:49:44,099 --> 00:49:45,300
[SPEAKER_03] dolje nije se vrijeđalo

1090
00:49:45,300 --> 00:49:46,219
[SPEAKER_03] branite li ovo ono,

1091
00:49:46,219 --> 00:49:48,340
[SPEAKER_03] ali vi kad uđete u pointu u suštinu,

1092
00:49:48,340 --> 00:49:50,199
[SPEAKER_03] on tamo udara na obitelj,

1093
00:49:50,199 --> 00:49:51,460
