1097
00:49:56,420 --> 00:49:58,239
[SPEAKER_03] Zato jer je taj lik bez kuće,

1098
00:49:58,239 --> 00:49:58,860
[SPEAKER_00] taj mačen,

1099
00:49:58,860 --> 00:49:59,719
[SPEAKER_00] taj nije,

1100
00:49:59,719 --> 00:50:01,860
[SPEAKER_00] znate što je njegova obitelj?

1101
00:50:01,860 --> 00:50:03,300
[SPEAKER_00] Muzej za gliste,

1102
00:50:03,300 --> 00:50:04,440
[SPEAKER_00] da, strašno,

1103
00:50:04,440 --> 00:50:05,199
[SPEAKER_00] ali ja bih,

1104
00:50:05,199 --> 00:50:06,400
