1107
00:50:10,219 --> 00:50:12,300
[SPEAKER_03] ne možete financirati ljude

1108
00:50:12,300 --> 00:50:14,400
[SPEAKER_03] koji udaraju na domovjski rat,

1109
00:50:14,400 --> 00:50:15,519
[SPEAKER_03] na hrvatske branitelje,

1110
00:50:15,519 --> 00:50:16,559
[SPEAKER_03] koji se sprdeju svjerov,

1111
00:50:16,559 --> 00:50:17,619
[SPEAKER_03] ali moram reći,

1112
00:50:17,619 --> 00:50:19,519
