1113
00:50:19,519 --> 00:50:22,119
[SPEAKER_03] imam ih naravno i među muslimanima,

1114
00:50:22,119 --> 00:50:23,260
[SPEAKER_03] neće mi to zamjeriti,

1115
00:50:24,460 --> 00:50:26,159
[SPEAKER_03] nikada nije napravio predstavu

1116
00:50:26,159 --> 00:50:27,119
[SPEAKER_03] gdje bi sprdao

1117
00:50:27,119 --> 00:50:29,059
[SPEAKER_03] Alaha Muhamed,

1118
00:50:29,059 --> 00:50:29,519
[SPEAKER_03] nikada,

1119
00:50:29,519 --> 00:50:30,239
[SPEAKER_03] dakle nikada,

1120
00:50:30,239 --> 00:50:31,559
[SPEAKER_03] znači s njima se ne sprda,

1121
00:50:31,559 --> 00:50:32,820
[SPEAKER_03] s islamom se ne sprda,

1122
00:50:32,820 --> 00:50:34,659
[SPEAKER_03] s židojima se ne sprda,

1123
00:50:34,659 --> 00:50:34,920
[SPEAKER_03] s ojima,

1124
00:50:34,920 --> 00:50:37,280
[SPEAKER_03] ali po kršćanima urinira je,

1125
00:50:37,280 --> 00:50:37,400
[SPEAKER_03] radi što očiš.

1126
00:50:37,400 --> 00:50:38,639
[SPEAKER_03] Zato jer zna da može,

1127
00:50:38,639 --> 00:50:39,480
[SPEAKER_03] može mu se,

1128
00:50:39,480 --> 00:50:41,900
[SPEAKER_00] ali sigurno ga ne financiraju

1129
00:50:41,900 --> 00:50:43,599
[SPEAKER_00] islamske države,

1130
00:50:43,599 --> 00:50:45,219
[SPEAKER_00] nego ga financiraju države

1131
00:50:45,219 --> 00:50:48,079
[SPEAKER_00] u kojima kao ima 90% uričini katu.

1132
00:50:48,079 --> 00:50:49,619
[SPEAKER_03] Ni na oboljen ga financiraju.

1133
00:50:49,619 --> 00:50:50,460
[SPEAKER_00] Sad kako će,

1134
00:50:50,460 --> 00:50:51,019
[SPEAKER_00] samo ovo,

1135
00:50:51,019 --> 00:50:52,059
[SPEAKER_00] znači,

1136
00:50:53,420 --> 00:50:54,840
[SPEAKER_00] vrijeđa Isusa Krista,

1137
00:50:54,840 --> 00:50:58,440
[SPEAKER_00] bljuje po hrvatskoj zastavi,

1138
00:50:58,440 --> 00:51:00,900
[SPEAKER_00] čak i doslovno.

1139
00:51:00,900 --> 00:51:05,219
[SPEAKER_00] Finansira ga pored oslovog

1140
00:51:05,219 --> 00:51:06,199
[SPEAKER_00] Ministarstva kulture,

1141
00:51:06,199 --> 00:51:07,719
[SPEAKER_00] na čijem je čelu ni na oboljen.

1142
00:51:07,719 --> 00:51:10,019
[SPEAKER_00] Tko su ljudi,

1143
00:51:10,019 --> 00:51:13,300
[SPEAKER_00] uključujući neke koje sam ja ovdje

1144
00:51:13,300 --> 00:51:14,880
[SPEAKER_00] promovirao i uveo u sabor,

1145
00:51:14,880 --> 00:51:15,800
[SPEAKER_00] poput Šipe i drugi,

1146
00:51:15,800 --> 00:51:16,880
[SPEAKER_00] i neću ih sad pljuvati.

1147
00:51:18,320 --> 00:51:20,079
[SPEAKER_00] pa je li vas sramota

1148
00:51:20,079 --> 00:51:22,500
[SPEAKER_00] ako ćete dići ruku

1149
00:51:22,500 --> 00:51:24,619
[SPEAKER_00] protiv njenog opaziva?

1150
00:51:24,619 --> 00:51:26,360
[SPEAKER_00] Je li ste toliko ljubomorni

1151
00:51:26,360 --> 00:51:28,800
[SPEAKER_00] na Miletića, Grbaju, Bulja i druge,

1152
00:51:28,800 --> 00:51:31,739
[SPEAKER_00] da samo zato što je njihova inicijativa

1153
00:51:31,739 --> 00:51:34,019
[SPEAKER_00] ćete se radije sakriti

1154
00:51:34,019 --> 00:51:35,840
[SPEAKER_00] pod kiklju

1155
00:51:35,840 --> 00:51:37,900
[SPEAKER_00] gospode ministarke?

1156
00:51:38,900 --> 00:51:40,980
[SPEAKER_00] Niste obični papci.

1157
00:51:40,980 --> 00:51:42,019
[SPEAKER_03] Izvolite.

1158
00:51:42,019 --> 00:51:44,340
[SPEAKER_03] Ja stvarno se nadam

1159
00:51:44,340 --> 00:51:46,340
[SPEAKER_03] da možda neće biti tako,

1160
00:51:46,340 --> 00:51:47,719
[SPEAKER_03] možda sam utopijski.

1161
00:51:47,719 --> 00:51:49,840
[SPEAKER_00] Ja sam apelirao sad na njih.

1162
00:51:49,840 --> 00:51:52,179
[SPEAKER_03] Pročitao sam negdje izjavu

1163
00:51:52,179 --> 00:51:53,579
[SPEAKER_03] gospodina Kukavice

1164
00:51:53,579 --> 00:51:55,380
[SPEAKER_03] koji je rekao...

1165
00:51:55,380 --> 00:51:56,760
[SPEAKER_00] Demonstrirao je protiv njega,

1166
00:51:56,760 --> 00:51:58,480
[SPEAKER_00] ali bar da ne dođe na glasu.

1167
00:51:58,480 --> 00:52:00,760
[SPEAKER_03] Sad, pa ćemo vidjeti šta će biti s tim.

1168
00:52:00,760 --> 00:52:02,739
[SPEAKER_00] Nemajte se bar pojaviti.

1169
00:52:02,739 --> 00:52:04,840
[SPEAKER_03] Nekako se nadam da

1170
00:52:04,840 --> 00:52:06,719
[SPEAKER_03] da će domovjski pokrep

1171
00:52:06,719 --> 00:52:07,539
[SPEAKER_03] pokazati ustav.

1172
00:52:08,280 --> 00:52:10,559
[SPEAKER_00] Pa eto, ja...

1173
00:52:10,559 --> 00:52:12,119
[SPEAKER_00] Živi bili pa vidjeli.

1174
00:52:12,119 --> 00:52:13,920
[SPEAKER_00] Malo sam emotivan, znate,

1175
00:52:13,920 --> 00:52:14,820
[SPEAKER_00] jer osjećam

1176
00:52:14,820 --> 00:52:17,599
[SPEAKER_00] i jedan dio vlastite odgovornosti.

1177
00:52:17,599 --> 00:52:21,260
[SPEAKER_03] Bradili ste u Saboru za dom spremni, ne?

1178
00:52:21,260 --> 00:52:23,360
[SPEAKER_03] Jesam, danas je bio kaos.

1179
00:52:23,360 --> 00:52:25,079
[SPEAKER_03] Dakle, jako je važno tu reći

1180
00:52:25,079 --> 00:52:26,199
[SPEAKER_03] hrvatskoj javnosti da zna.

1181
00:52:26,199 --> 00:52:27,780
[SPEAKER_03] Meni često se znaju ljudi javiti.

1182
00:52:27,780 --> 00:52:29,500
[SPEAKER_03] Imam puno mlađe populacije

1183
00:52:29,500 --> 00:52:30,119
[SPEAKER_03] koja me prati.

1184
00:52:30,119 --> 00:52:31,139
[SPEAKER_03] I onda onaj kažu meni,

1185
00:52:31,139 --> 00:52:33,380
[SPEAKER_03] Marine, pa joj, pa ne moraš sad opet

1186
00:52:33,380 --> 00:52:35,420
[SPEAKER_03] za dom spremni, ne moraš obranitelja.

1187
00:52:35,420 --> 00:52:37,619
[SPEAKER_03] Ima toliko tema koje su na važne.

1188
00:52:37,659 --> 00:52:39,239
[SPEAKER_03] Mi o svim tim tema govorimo.

1189
00:52:39,239 --> 00:52:41,659
[SPEAKER_03] Od mirovina, radništva, plaća, poreza,

1190
00:52:41,659 --> 00:52:43,380
[SPEAKER_03] sustava, migracija,

1191
00:52:43,380 --> 00:52:45,619
[SPEAKER_03] nadziranja naših poruka

1192
00:52:45,619 --> 00:52:47,039
[SPEAKER_03] preko WhatsApp-a, kriptiranih.

1193
00:52:47,039 --> 00:52:48,239
[SPEAKER_03] Dakle, mi o svemu tome govorimo.

1194
00:52:48,420 --> 00:52:50,980
[SPEAKER_03] Ali, ako SDP i možemo,

1195
00:52:50,980 --> 00:52:53,559
[SPEAKER_03] idu danas pitanja Plenković u njegovim ministrijima.

1196
00:52:53,559 --> 00:52:57,440
[SPEAKER_03] I on je orkestriran od prvog dok zadnje krenu.

1197
00:52:57,440 --> 00:52:59,960
[SPEAKER_03] Kažnjavanje za dom spremni.

1198
00:52:59,960 --> 00:53:02,039
[SPEAKER_03] Ustašizacija Hrvatske.

1199
00:53:02,159 --> 00:53:03,699
[SPEAKER_03] Fašizam, Rastuči, Benčička,

1200
00:53:03,699 --> 00:53:06,000
[SPEAKER_03] Urliče u Saboru u Hrvatskoj.

1201
00:53:06,000 --> 00:53:07,559
[SPEAKER_03] Protiv Tomsona.

1202
00:53:07,559 --> 00:53:09,440
[SPEAKER_03] 500 tisuća ljudi na hipodromu.

1203
00:53:09,440 --> 00:53:11,099
[SPEAKER_03] 200 tisuća, dakle, u Sinju.

1204
00:53:11,099 --> 00:53:12,179
[SPEAKER_03] Pa, dosta vas je.

1205
00:53:12,179 --> 00:53:13,659
[SPEAKER_03] Dakle, ja to nisam mogo prešutiti.

1206
00:53:13,659 --> 00:53:14,260
[SPEAKER_03] Neću nikada.

1207
00:53:14,360 --> 00:53:17,199
[SPEAKER_00] Hajde da vidimo, Biletića, kako izgleda kad ne može šutjet,

1208
00:53:17,199 --> 00:53:18,840
[SPEAKER_00] a meni tako drago.

1209
00:53:18,840 --> 00:53:22,000
[SPEAKER_00] I žao što ja nisam, ono, mlad.

1210
00:53:22,000 --> 00:53:23,940
[SPEAKER_00] Pa da kažem, mladi su za tebe,

1211
00:53:23,940 --> 00:53:27,039
[SPEAKER_00] ali danas su ovi dečki i cureke su pripremale prilog

1212
00:53:27,039 --> 00:53:30,539
[SPEAKER_00] i pripremali, oni su mlađi od 20 godina,

1213
00:53:30,539 --> 00:53:32,480
[SPEAKER_00] rekli ovo, pusti, ovo nam se sviđa.

1214
00:53:32,480 --> 00:53:33,579
[SPEAKER_00] Tako da vidite.

1215
00:53:33,579 --> 00:53:34,360
[SPEAKER_03] Hvala.

1216
00:53:34,360 --> 00:53:43,019
[SPEAKER_03] Ne slažemo se sa Ljevicom koja ne želi,

1217
00:53:43,420 --> 00:53:46,019
[SPEAKER_03] ne želi se očitovati o zločinima komunizma,

1218
00:53:46,019 --> 00:53:47,400
[SPEAKER_03] prave se blesavi,

1219
00:53:47,400 --> 00:53:51,039
[SPEAKER_03] a mi u klubu Mosta nikad se nećemo odreći

1220
00:53:51,039 --> 00:53:51,980
[SPEAKER_03] hrvatskih branitelja,

1221
00:53:51,980 --> 00:53:54,619
[SPEAKER_03] oni koji su ginuli za ovu državu,

1222
00:53:54,619 --> 00:53:55,900
[SPEAKER_03] hrvatsku državu,

1223
00:53:55,900 --> 00:53:58,300
[SPEAKER_03] koji su dali svoje živote,

1224
00:53:58,300 --> 00:54:00,400
[SPEAKER_03] a dok su ginuli, uzvikivali su mnogi.

1225
00:54:00,400 --> 00:54:04,159
[SPEAKER_03] I pozdrav za dom spremni napose naši momci iz HOS-a.

1226
00:54:04,159 --> 00:54:11,019
[SPEAKER_00] I šta da vam sad kažem,

1227
00:54:11,480 --> 00:54:14,800
[SPEAKER_00] imat ćemo naravno i jednog snažnog gosta

1228
00:54:14,800 --> 00:54:16,460
[SPEAKER_00] i posebnu emisiju o njemu,

1229
00:54:16,460 --> 00:54:19,420
[SPEAKER_00] riječ je Marku Perkoviću Thompsonu,

1230
00:54:19,420 --> 00:54:22,239
[SPEAKER_00] pa nemamo vremena puštati prekrasne kadrove,

1231
00:54:22,239 --> 00:54:23,519
[SPEAKER_00] a nismo zaboravili,

1232
00:54:23,519 --> 00:54:24,820
[SPEAKER_00] sa hipodroma,

1233
00:54:24,820 --> 00:54:27,079
[SPEAKER_00] ali onih 500 tisuća,

1234
00:54:27,079 --> 00:54:31,920
[SPEAKER_00] od kojih je zapravo više od pola mladih,

1235
00:54:33,199 --> 00:54:36,519
[SPEAKER_00] baš njih briga šta misli drugarica

1236
00:54:36,519 --> 00:54:37,500
[SPEAKER_00] Hajdi Dončić.

1237
00:54:37,500 --> 00:54:40,500
[SPEAKER_00] Ne zanima njih ljevica uopće.

1238
00:54:40,500 --> 00:54:43,440
[SPEAKER_00] I vidjet će se sve više,

1239
00:54:43,440 --> 00:54:45,159
[SPEAKER_00] će biti buđenja i bit će to dobro.

1240
00:54:45,159 --> 00:54:46,860
[SPEAKER_00] A sad da bi se probudili,

1241
00:54:46,860 --> 00:54:48,039
[SPEAKER_00] prvi korak je,

1242
00:54:48,039 --> 00:54:51,300
[SPEAKER_00] pa i ovo da u mostu imate izbore,

1243
00:54:51,300 --> 00:54:53,719
[SPEAKER_00] pa onda čujem da idu neke zajedničke platforme,

1244
00:54:53,719 --> 00:54:54,960
[SPEAKER_00] nešto i učite od ljevice,

1245
00:54:54,960 --> 00:54:56,460
[SPEAKER_00] da budete na 15-20,

1246
00:54:57,159 --> 00:54:59,460
[SPEAKER_00] a ne svi zajedno na manjim postocima.

1247
00:54:59,460 --> 00:55:02,780
[SPEAKER_00] Prošli put kad ste bili,

1248
00:55:02,780 --> 00:55:05,460
[SPEAKER_00] od tada se svašta dogodilo.

1249
00:55:05,460 --> 00:55:07,219
[SPEAKER_00] Rijeka je osvojila dvostruku Krunu,

1250
00:55:07,219 --> 00:55:08,880
[SPEAKER_00] tu ste ispali.

1251
00:55:08,880 --> 00:55:10,440
[SPEAKER_00] Đalović otišao.

1252
00:55:10,440 --> 00:55:12,440
[SPEAKER_00] Ne, otišao je Đalović,

1253
00:55:12,440 --> 00:55:14,000
[SPEAKER_00] odlazi i Petrov.

1254
00:55:14,000 --> 00:55:14,960
[SPEAKER_00] Tko ostaje?

1255
00:55:14,960 --> 00:55:16,039
[SPEAKER_00] Šta je s mostom?

1256
00:55:16,039 --> 00:55:16,699
[SPEAKER_03] Gdje je most?

1257
00:55:16,699 --> 00:55:18,519
[SPEAKER_03] Ostaju mostovci, jeli?

1258
00:55:18,519 --> 00:55:20,340
[SPEAKER_03] Dakle, stvarno, evo,

1259
00:55:20,340 --> 00:55:22,300
[SPEAKER_03] opet jedna ekskluziva kod vas.

1260
00:55:22,300 --> 00:55:23,280
[SPEAKER_03] Baš želim to reći.

1261
00:55:23,280 --> 00:55:25,940
[SPEAKER_03] Nisam novinarima uopće na ovakav način govorio.

1262
00:55:26,760 --> 00:55:30,199
[SPEAKER_03] Kod nas trenutno jedino Nikola Grmoja

1263
00:55:30,199 --> 00:55:32,820
[SPEAKER_03] se kandidirao za predsjednika stranke.

1264
00:55:32,820 --> 00:55:37,760
[SPEAKER_03] Mene su mediji u stvari tu cijelo vrijeme stavljali i gurali.

1265
00:55:37,760 --> 00:55:39,539
[SPEAKER_03] Dakle, vi nemate nijedan moj status,

1266
00:55:39,539 --> 00:55:41,699
[SPEAKER_03] nijednu moju izjavu gdje sam ja rekao

1267
00:55:41,699 --> 00:55:42,900
[SPEAKER_03] kandidiram se, jeli?

1268
00:55:42,900 --> 00:55:43,900
[SPEAKER_03] Dakle, nema je.

1269
00:55:43,900 --> 00:55:45,219
[SPEAKER_03] Znači, nije vas ponjelo.

1270
00:55:45,219 --> 00:55:46,360
[SPEAKER_03] Zato je nisam to napravio.

1271
00:55:46,360 --> 00:55:48,139
[SPEAKER_03] Ne, ne, gledajte ovako.

1272
00:55:48,139 --> 00:55:49,980
[SPEAKER_03] Ajmo biti racionalni.

1273
00:55:49,980 --> 00:55:51,760
[SPEAKER_03] Važna je razboritost u životu.

1274
00:55:51,760 --> 00:55:54,079
[SPEAKER_03] Inače je i dar duha svetoga.

1275
00:55:54,079 --> 00:55:56,519
[SPEAKER_03] Sad koliko je imam, ne znam,

1276
00:55:56,519 --> 00:55:58,579
[SPEAKER_03] ali evo, dakle, razboritost jako važna.

1277
00:55:58,579 --> 00:56:01,960
[SPEAKER_03] Božo je vodio deset godina stranku

1278
00:56:01,960 --> 00:56:04,280
[SPEAKER_03] i treba mu skinuti kapu jer je sačuvao most.

1279
00:56:04,280 --> 00:56:07,019
[SPEAKER_03] Nisam siguran da je netko od nas ga možda vodio

1280
00:56:07,019 --> 00:56:09,079
[SPEAKER_03] kroz sve situacije kroz koje su bile

1281
00:56:09,079 --> 00:56:10,699
[SPEAKER_03] da bi smo mi tu opstali.

1282
00:56:10,840 --> 00:56:13,400
[SPEAKER_03] On ima svojih mana, naravno, kao i svi mi,

1283
00:56:13,400 --> 00:56:14,699
[SPEAKER_03] ali ima ogromne kvalitete.

1284
00:56:14,699 --> 00:56:15,840
[SPEAKER_03] On je sačuvao stranku.

1285
00:56:15,840 --> 00:56:18,840
[SPEAKER_03] Mi smo tu cijelo vrijeme treća, četvrta politička opcija,

1286
00:56:18,840 --> 00:56:22,760
[SPEAKER_03] dakle, što nije lako zadržati u ovim turbulentnim vremenima

1287
00:56:22,760 --> 00:56:24,840
[SPEAKER_03] političkim i sve u kojima živimo.

1288
00:56:25,400 --> 00:56:28,300
[SPEAKER_03] S druge strane, osnivači mosta,

1289
00:56:28,300 --> 00:56:29,960
[SPEAKER_03] to je svega nekoliko ljudi,

1290
00:56:29,960 --> 00:56:32,599
[SPEAKER_03] najistaknutiji su Božo Petrov i Nikola Grmoja,

1291
00:56:32,599 --> 00:56:35,800
[SPEAKER_03] jer je Nikola Grmoja u stvari došao Boži Petrovu

1292
00:56:35,800 --> 00:56:37,500
[SPEAKER_03] na jednoj terasi u Metkoviću na kafiću

1293
00:56:37,500 --> 00:56:38,739
[SPEAKER_03] i rekao, idemo srušiti jambu,

1294
00:56:38,739 --> 00:56:39,920
[SPEAKER_03] ajmo osnovati stranku, most.

1295
00:56:40,280 --> 00:56:42,739
[SPEAKER_03] I tako je krenula, znači, nekako ideja sada skrati.

1296
00:56:42,739 --> 00:56:45,699
[SPEAKER_03] Je, slažem se, ali ja sam pet godina u politici,

1297
00:56:45,699 --> 00:56:48,059
[SPEAKER_03] a oni su od prvog dana, oni su tu stranku osnivali.

1298
00:56:48,059 --> 00:56:50,159
[SPEAKER_03] I vi, kad gledate iz te perspektive,

1299
00:56:50,159 --> 00:56:53,820
[SPEAKER_03] prirodno i logično da sada u ovoj situaciji,

1300
00:56:53,820 --> 00:56:56,500
[SPEAKER_03] u tom nekom, ajmo možda to tako nazvati,

1301
00:56:56,500 --> 00:56:58,639
[SPEAKER_03] prijelaznom razdoblju jačanja naše stranke,

1302
00:56:58,639 --> 00:57:01,179
[SPEAKER_03] što mi vjerujemo, da to bude jedan od osnivača.

1303
00:57:01,179 --> 00:57:02,880
[SPEAKER_03] Pa nikolu niko ne može pobjediti,

1304
00:57:02,880 --> 00:57:05,260
[SPEAKER_03] razumijete koliko je ovo članova u Dalmaciji,

1305
00:57:05,260 --> 00:57:06,059
[SPEAKER_03] nego Božom.

1306
